# Keep the Docker build context (and CDK asset staging) small, and prevent the
# recursive cdk.out-inside-cdk.out copy. The backend image only needs source +
# workspace manifests; it installs its own dependencies.
**/node_modules
**/cdk.out
.git
.github
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.turbo
apps/ios
*.log
.DS_Store
**/*.xcuserstate
